  <section class="simple-section full-desktop full-tablet">
    <h2 class="h1">
      Unmatched Load and <br /> Endurance
    </h2>
    <p class="paragraph-1">
      The B2 is built for heavy-duty industrial tasks. It boasts a maximum
      standing load of 120 kg and can continuously walk with a payload of over
      40 kg. Its ultra-large capacity 2250Wh battery provides an
      industry-leading endurance of over 4 hours with a 20kg load, ensuring it
      can complete long-duration, critical missions without interruption.
    </p>
    <div class="media-wrapper">
      <video playsinline muted loop preload="metadata" class="media">
        <source src="/videos/b2/0.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="simple-section full-tablet">
    <h2 class="h1">
      Extreme Mobility and <br class="br-mobile br-tablet" /> All-<br
        class="br-desktop"
      />Terrain Adaptation
    </h2>
