      With a maximum joint torque of 360 N.m, the B2 achieves extreme
      performance and stability. It can effortlessly climb stairs of 20-25 cm
      continuously, tackle slopes greater than 45°, and even jump a distance of
      over 1.6 meters. This level of dynamic capability ensures stable travel on
      slippery, uneven, or complex industrial terrains.
    </p>
    <div class="media-wrapper">
